{"tid":1278663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭想當無死過人","createTime":"2019-07-02T13:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:40:16.000Z","uid":95173,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8538209fca844e08a31091fe2ffdcd893db15b36","tid":1278663,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"睇翻琴晚林鄭月娥咁急見記者<br />\n動員身邊「愛將」振振有詞 <br />\n再次飾演人肉錄音機<br />\n<br />\n對記者提問3位年輕人為政權自殺一事<br />\n視若無睹充耳不聞<br />\n裝模作樣「咋」唔知<br />\n<br />\n以為自己可以成為第二代六四事件領導人<br />\n蓋住社會聲音當無發生過<br />\n呢種手法等於無視以死對極權嘅生命<br />\n<br />\n你以為唔理香港人訴求唔理社會崩潰嘅情緒<br />\n後世嘅人會唔知你林鄭今日有幾黑心有幾毒？<br />\n<br />\n歷史一定會寫<br />\n<br />\n仲會寫得清清楚楚<br />\n因為我地香港人會追究到底"},{"pid":"d56be7ccb7e9cfe32ee8673f56b6712484a620a7","tid":1278663,"uid":95173,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"我地嘅訴求一個都未回應過<br />\n你想就咁有下台階？<br />\n痴心妄想"},{"pid":"0c47d832ee2cb04519ba12d8e3e6362e47815de3","tid":1278663,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d66c8677b3269dc8c84dbf161c6139be0fdfae98","tid":1278663,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"732b9832159b6083ad201c7d4e2ca46a85991f7f","tid":1278663,"uid":46758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"落地獄"},{"pid":"a8a70474e62b2f8885be919e37e43344f35ee53e","tid":1278663,"uid":95173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"口口聲聲話林同佳一案聲討<br />\n作為媽媽嘅你<br />\n只應共產黨兒女做仔女？"},{"pid":"97844d8d914b7ed998764d78eafe15dcb66f0c50","tid":1278663,"uid":95173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"我地講咩對你黎講都係無用<br />\n因為傷害唔到你<br />\n但你以後會遺臭萬年"},{"pid":"b15798286525b5b6f2014833db0e734ef8de7edb","tid":1278663,"uid":66683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被